Smart Navigator Privacy Policy
Last updated: June 2026

Smart Navigator does not collect, transmit, or share any personal data.

All data stored by this extension (widget position, visibility preference, recent search terms)
is stored locally on your device using chrome.storage.local and is never sent to any server.

The extension reads page content only to perform local text search at your explicit request.
This content is never stored or transmitted.

